YET ANOTHER DUMB ONESHOT MAP

As the title says. A quick little map I made in my spare time because I had some cut features from bhop_pure_aids floating around in my head. It took me about 3 hours, so there's not much to say about it. textures are noclipper's textures. Like all my other maps, the start zone is the green block, the end zone is the red block. Enjoy.

Length: 10 - 30 seconds
Difficulty: Hard
